"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-29-olympic-boxers-heartbreaking-reaction-shock-loss-i-feel-like-a-failure-im-sorry-21318930\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Australia's medal hopeful in men's lightweight boxing, Harry Garside, suffered a surprise defeat in the round of 16 and gave a heartbreaking response, saying: 'I feel like a failure, I am so sorry.'\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Garside won bronze at the Tokyo Games and is a formerCommonwealth Gamesgold medallist, giving up a pro career to focus on gold inParis.\", \"from\": 200, \"to\": 335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, he was beaten in his opening bout against Hungary's Richard Kovacs and the 27-year-old gave a tear-jerking interview after the painful loss.\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 388, \"end\": 395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.6352388475880903, \"rank\": 0.5659708535034131, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Aussie spoke openly aboutmental healthstruggles ahead of Paris,saying he has had suicidal thoughts in the past,and is now worried for his immediate future, which he expects to be 'quite challenging'.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 549, \"end\": 554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999774142909, \"rank\": 2.258559900041516e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's crazy.\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two decades dedicated to one dream and it's all over just like that,' he said, viaFox Sports.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I feel pretty numb right now.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am sure the next month or two will be quite challenging, quite hard.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I fear for my mind, it gets a better of me.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like I have let myself down and letAustraliadown mate, but what do you do?\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Australia is such a sporting nation, and I am so sorry.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1032, \"end\": 1041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.6748285235116148, \"rank\": 0.3557586764927917, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Honestly.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like a failure right now.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like \\u2026 I do not even know what to say.'\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Garside thankfully did see some positives and thanked his family and team, while sending a message to children who may hope to achieve their own sporting dreams.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Thank you so much Australia.\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It really means a lot,' he continued.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I know sportsmen are just supposed to say the right things right now.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And thank you so much but deep down inside, mate, I fear for what the next couple of months looks like for myself.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1595, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And there'll truly be some dark times, mate.\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I gotta prepare for that now.\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have got to thank my coach.\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's been there since I was nine years old, 18 years in my corner, and I love that man to bits,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1808, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'My mum and dad.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone back home, 3140 Lilydale, all of Australia.\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1869, \"end\": 1878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.6748285235116148, \"rank\": 0.3557586764927917, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The support I have had online is unbelievable.\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'And I really thought that I could win that gold medal, but that's a failure, right?\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 2012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That sport, that's life.\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I will get back up after a few months and see what's next.\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2100, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Can I just say something to the kids out there?\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was seven years old two decades ago when this dream started.\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The man that I have become on that journey over 20 years is unbelievable.'\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFaceboo